{"tid":379591,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩返屋企 係路邊見到班廢老係到拜神","createTime":"2017-08-29T12:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T13:34:30.000Z","uid":19638,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb8f932a1994ba648dd17542f74901921ad5ee2","tid":379591,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的 岩岩放工 本身個人都攰攰地<br />\n行緊返屋企個時 路邊有班廢老妹下妹下咁係到燒野<br />\n望真d 原來拜緊神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就二話不說 攞手頭上枝水一野潑落個堆元寶蠟燭<br />\n再係地下攞左個蘋果來食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身想攞到埋碟叉雞 不過算 成堆灰係面頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟著望住班廢老望住我嘴渺渺咁 係到口upup 唔知講咩春 我就一路啤住佢地 行到路口先無再望佢地<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解 心情好爽 仲R到舊蘋果食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e470295b35c9e2bd09831756230b512979163b3d","tid":379591,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075e655833ba9674687b304e15ed3fdd9e567ae6","tid":379591,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:52:54.000Z","msg":"Ok u win"},{"pid":"0da4f040fa6027e8846dc9104ac72c318d0da2f0","tid":379591,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪興奮過度 <br />\n<br />\n而家有d頭暈頭痛 <br />\n<br />\n望野周不時有紅光"},{"pid":"a840aa4e0f9cbd58b17f47148588798876c7f57d","tid":379591,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:55:44.000Z","msg":"7月14 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你小心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0538daabe880e8002dd57668ac0fef102b800540","tid":379591,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"好波ching<img src=\"/assets/face